# Antigravity Awesome Skills (local library)

This repo includes a local copy of **Antigravity Awesome Skills** at:

- `.agents/skills/`
- Skills live under `.agents/skills/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`
- Catalog / index:
  - `.agents/skills/CATALOG.md`
  - `.agents/skills/skills_index.json`
  - Cursor-specific usage docs: `.agents/skills/docs/users/cursor-skills.md`

## How to use skills during this project

- When the user asks for a workflow (“plan”, “debug”, “refactor”, “testing”, “security”, “deploy”, etc.), prefer applying one of these skills.
- Pick a skill by:
  - Searching the catalog first (`CATALOG.md`) for a matching name/topic
  - Then reading the corresponding `SKILL.md` and following its steps

## Conventions

- Treat skills as **operating instructions** (constraints + steps), not as text to paste verbatim.
- If a skill conflicts with project constraints (dry-run safety, no pushing, no secrets), project constraints win.

